{"tid":1293121,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"[L.O.V.E] NU'EST 討論區(4) 終於人齊喇! 0727 香港演唱會見!","createTime":"2019-07-07T14:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T17:02:37.000Z","uid":252325,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"194adc7c4369f6308febd23c84e79763c5407903","tid":1293121,"uid":252325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:56:01.000Z","msg":"#1<br />\n召集所有鐘意NU'EST的面孔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.allkpop.com/upload/2019/03/content/171650/nuestjpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allkpop.com%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2Fcontent%2F171650%2Fnuestjpg.jpg&h=ac1b858f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNU'EST（韓語：뉴이스트），韓國Pledis娛樂於2012年推出的首組男子團體，成員有Aron、JR、白虎、旼炫及Ren。<br />\n<br />\nNU'EST全稱為「NU, Establish, Style, Tempo」，意為「Establishing a new style of music（建立音樂的新風格）」。<br />\n<br />\n歌迷官方名稱為「L.O.&Lambda;.E」，取自韓文團名「뉴이스트」的子音字母「ㄴㅇㅅㅌ」，唸法同英文單字「LOVE」。<br />\n<br />\n官方應援色過去使用螢光淡粉紅色，2018年1月1日正式公告為Deep Teal #00313C和Vivid Pink #E31C79。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/002012_ca383ae7fcc9441ee7e4e47668e25800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F002012_ca383ae7fcc9441ee7e4e47668e25800.jpg&h=407df4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出道曲《FACE》為韓國男子團體出道曲於YouTube頻道最高觀看次數記錄保持者，但2014至15年間過長的海外活動，導致韓國本土的歌迷嚴重流失。<br />\n<br />\n在聲勢極度低迷的2017年初，除了因腳傷休養的Aron外，四名成員（JR、白虎、旼炫、Ren）參加《PRODUCE 101 第二季》，憑藉節目中的表現使NU'EST重新獲得大眾矚目。在節目總決賽中，旼炫入選為出道組Wanna One成員。而另外四名成員組成小分隊「NU'EST W」於下半年回歸歌壇，NU'EST-W的「W」代表着「等待（Waiting you）」，成員將等待旼炫完成Wanna One的活動後歸隊，重新以完整體的形式展開活動，同時也意味着成員等待和歌迷重逢的一刻。<br />\n<br />\n2019年, 旼炫完成Wanna One 為期1年半合約後正式回歸Nu'est, 2019年3月15日團體度過了第7週年,並推出了單曲A Song for you, 是自2016年以來首支5人完全體的單曲; 2019年4月12-14日於首爾奧林匹克體操競技場舉辦首個團體專屬演唱會;並於2019年4月29日正式以5人姿態回歸並推出最新專輯&quot;Happily Ever After&quot;; 並於宣傳期成功為團隊奪得3個音樂榜之一位,結束其長達出道後2611天取得首個一位的紀錄; 組合亦會於2019年下半年開始展開其首個世界巡迴演唱會,展開組合新的一頁。"},{"pid":"e0abad2032d6804f467e7d77152db112d4e97037","tid":1293121,"uid":166903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"我都開咗添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced3ef0b251ad2838fe4741c9f31fa797126a0c9","tid":1293121,"uid":252325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"#2<br />\n成員資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C4J7Q3hUkAAX06A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC4J7Q3hUkAAX06A.jpg&h=974a0952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAron (아론)<br />\n本名: 郭英敏 Kwak Young Min Aaron<br />\n出生地: 美國加利福尼亞州洛杉磯<br />\n出生日期: 1993年5月21日（24歲）<br />\n血型: A<br />\n隊內擔當: 副唱、副Rapper、大哥<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/c8/c5/48/c8c548400c5d0f3ee703eccc837bf2cf--nu-est-jr-kpop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2Fc8%2Fc5%2F48%2Fc8c548400c5d0f3ee703eccc837bf2cf--nu-est-jr-kpop.jpg&h=ba0295ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJR (제이알)<br />\n本名: 金鐘炫 Kim Jong Hyeon <br />\n出生地: 南韓江原道江陵市<br />\n出生日期: 1995年6月8日（22歲）<br />\n血型: O<br />\n隊內擔當: 隊長、主Rapper、主領舞<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.allkpop.com/upload/2017/08/content/NUEST_Baekho_1503451526_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allkpop.com%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2Fcontent%2FNUEST_Baekho_1503451526_2.jpg&h=5b1540b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白虎 (백호)<br />\n本名: 姜東昊 Kang Dong Ho<br />\n出生地: 南韓濟州特別自治道<br />\n出生日期: 1995年7月21日（22歲）<br />\n血型: AB<br />\n隊內擔當: 第一主唱<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/d5/06/b9/d506b9eb74205abc29cc6e58a1a9a470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fd5%2F06%2Fb9%2Fd506b9eb74205abc29cc6e58a1a9a470.jpg&h=b0ab179a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旼炫 (민현)<br />\n本名:黃旼炫 Hwang Min Hyun <br />\n出生地: 南韓釜山廣域市<br />\n出生日期: 1995年8月9日（22歲）<br />\n血型: O<br />\n隊內擔當: 領唱、形象<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.allkpop.com/upload/2017/08/af_org/23205557/NUEST-Ren.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allkpop.com%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2Faf_org%2F23205557%2FNUEST-Ren.jpg&h=717e3107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRen (렌)<br />\n本名: 崔珉起 Choi Min Gi<br />\n出生地: 南韓釜山廣域市<br />\n出生日期: 1995年11月3日（21歲）<br />\n血型: O<br />\n隊內擔當: 副唱、門面"},{"pid":"36605536259bab60ff628ba27ef7935f9ef9e8c3","tid":1293121,"uid":252325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0abad2032d6804f467e7d77152db112d4e97037","tid":1293121,"uid":166903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"我都開咗添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"噢撈,唔知點解我一路都SEARCH唔到你果個POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇LINK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c5ab5359ad1986866586ba70f9779f7113dc21","tid":1293121,"uid":257585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n終於唔係dejavu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680ffb83ec212808dc4bcd100609128ddb6d3d69","tid":1293121,"uid":166903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"推邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97458d1d0cea4a99d4e7f2345121c8bbaea4294","tid":1293121,"uid":257585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"680ffb83ec212808dc4bcd100609128ddb6d3d69","tid":1293121,"uid":166